00:44:01,388 --> 00:44:02,378
Hi.

584
00:44:05,727 --> 00:44:07,321
Walter. Thank you for coming.

585
00:44:07,395 --> 00:44:09,365
Of course.

586
00:44:09,631 --> 00:44:11,692
