602
00:45:11,462 --> 00:45:12,726
The lights are always on.

603
00:45:14,298 --> 00:45:15,324
You need anything?

604
00:45:15,400 --> 00:45:17,802
No. I just want to get out of here.

605
00:45:19,137 --> 00:45:22,007
Well... Zainab and I met
with a lawyer today.

606
00:45:22,074 --> 00:45:24,010
Yes? What did he say?

607
00:45:24,076 --> 00:45:26,741
Well, he's... he's gonna
stop by tomorrow and see you.

608
00:45:29,148 --> 00:45:33,783
Tarek. Zainab said
that you were denied asylum.

609
00:45:33,853 --> 00:45:35,413
