612
00:45:39,759 --> 00:45:41,251
Yeah.

613
00:45:41,327 --> 00:45:42,420
In Michigan.

614
00:45:42,495 --> 00:45:44,192
Yeah. We did everything they told us to.

615
00:45:44,264 --> 00:45:45,493
Okay.

616
00:45:47,468 --> 00:45:48,902
Let's go, man. You gotta get off.

617
00:45:48,968 --> 00:45:50,437
