00:46:00,448 --> 00:46:01,781
Good-bye, my friend.

624
00:46:01,850 --> 00:46:02,840
Good-bye.

625
00:46:14,529 --> 00:46:15,462
I'll see you tomorrow.

626
00:46:15,530 --> 00:46:17,193
Okay. Bye.

