You can stay here.

631
00:46:35,384 --> 00:46:37,047
I think it's better I leave.

632
00:46:38,054 --> 00:46:41,516
Um... you know how to reach me
if you need to.

633
00:46:45,395 --> 00:46:48,299
Is it okay if I leave
Tarek's things here for now?

634
00:46:49,299 --> 00:46:54,173
Uh, my cousin's place is...
not very big.

635
00:46:55,238 --> 00:46:56,468
Yes, of course.

636
00:46:57,575 --> 00:46:58,804
Thank you.

637
00:47:20,899 --> 00:47:21,889
Hello?

638
00:47:23,202 --> 00:47:24,602
Oh. Hi, Charles.

639
00:47:26,105 --> 00:47:28,098
Oh. Wait. I'm sorry. Wha... What?

640
00:47:29,943 --> 00:47:31,845
Yeah. The conference went very well.

641
00:47:31,911 --> 00:47:33,380
Yes.

642
00:47:33,446 --> 00:47:37,044
No, uh, actually, I'm still in New York,
and I'm doing some research for my book.

643
00:47:37,117 --> 00:47:38,380
Why?

644
00:47:39,452 --> 00:47:41,081
When's the meeting?

645
00:47:41,154 --> 00:47:42,554
Wha...

646
00:47:42,622 --> 00:47:43,555
Oh. Okay.

647
00:47:43,623 --> 00:47:45,890
All right. I... I'll, um...

648
00:47:45,960 --> 00:47:48,396
I'll leave first thing tomorrow.

649
00:47:48,462 --> 00:47:51,228
Yeah. I'll see you at 3. Bye.

650
00:48:01,309 --> 00:48:03,302
I thought you said
you went to the hearing.

651
00:48:03,377 --> 00:48:05,074
We did. I remember it.

652
00:48:05,147 --> 00:48:07,584
Well, then why is there
a final order out on you?

653
00:48:07,649 --> 00:48:09,243
He didn't know yet. He just said

654
00:48:09,318 --> 00:48:12,290
that unless they can find a way
to reopen the case quickly,

655
00:48:12,354 --> 00:48:13,583
they're going to deport me.

656
00:48:15,157 --> 00:48:17,423
I don't even understand it.

657
00:48:17,492 --> 00:48:20,430
Walter, there are guys
who have been in here for years.

658
00:48:20,495 --> 00:48:22,260
I can't do that, Walter. I'll go crazy.

659
00:48:22,331 --> 00:48:25,600
He's trying to deal with the case
as quickly as possible.

660
00:48:25,668 --> 00:48:27,604
I know. I know. It's...

661
00:48:27,670 --> 00:48:29,139
It's just...

662
00:48:30,206 --> 00:48:32,472
Look, maybe we
should call your mother.

663
00:48:32,542 --> 00:48:35,982
No. No. I don't want her to worry.

664
00:48:37,513 --> 00:48:38,503
Yeah.

665
00:48:43,020 --> 00:48:44,489
Tarek, um...

666
00:48:46,256 --> 00:48:47,622
I have to go back to Connecticut.

667
00:48:47,691 --> 00:48:49,126
When?

668
00:48:49,193 --> 00:48:50,456
Tomorrow.

669
00:48:50,527 --> 00:48:52,998
But I'll be reachable
