678
00:49:11,616 --> 00:49:12,642
No.

679
00:49:14,720 --> 00:49:17,715
Okay, but listen to that Fela CD.
That will help you.

680
00:49:17,990 --> 00:49:19,721
- I promise.
- I will. I will.

681
00:49:22,229 --> 00:49:24,529
So show me what you...
you've been working on.

682
00:49:24,597 --> 00:49:26,328
What?

683
00:49:26,399 --> 00:49:28,232
