695
00:50:37,808 --> 00:50:39,333
I'm looking for my son.

696
00:50:39,409 --> 00:50:40,571
Excuse me.

697
00:50:40,644 --> 00:50:42,807
Uh, are...
are you Tarek's mother?

698
00:50:44,548 --> 00:50:45,538
Yes.

699
00:50:45,616 --> 00:50:49,078
Well, this is Tarek's apartment.

700
00:50:49,154 --> 00:50:50,247
I j...

701
00:50:50,321 --> 00:50:51,812
I share the apartment with him.

702
00:50:53,491 --> 00:50:55,586
He didn't mention
that he lived with someone.

703
00:50:56,828 --> 00:50:58,353
Well, I'm not here very often.

704
00:50:58,429 --> 00:50:59,830
I... I live in Connecticut.

705
00:51:00,832 --> 00:51:02,597
Is Tarek here?

706
00:51:03,602 --> 00:51:05,765
No. He's not here now.

707
00:51:05,837 --> 00:51:07,830
Uh, come in... please.

708
00:51:10,675 --> 00:51:11,837
Please.

709
00:51:14,180 --> 00:51:15,239
Thank you.

710
00:51:23,190 --> 00:51:25,456
Oh, my name is Walter. Walter Vale.

711
00:51:25,525 --> 00:51:27,290
I'm... I'm Mouna Khalil.

712
00:51:27,361 --> 00:51:29,388
I'm sorry to show up unannounced.

713
00:51:30,563 --> 00:51:32,260
My son hasn't called me for five days.

714
00:51:32,332 --> 00:51:34,860
I keep trying his cell phone,
but he doesn't answer.

715
00:51:36,536 --> 00:51:37,799
Would you like to sit down?

716
00:51:37,871 --> 00:51:38,861
Thank you.

717
00:51:57,226 --> 00:51:58,819
Mr. Vale?

718
00:51:58,893 --> 00:52:00,362
Is my son all right?

719
00:52:00,428 --> 00:52:01,418
Yes.

720
00:52:02,898 --> 00:52:04,230
