734
00:52:49,614 --> 00:52:50,604
Okay.

735
00:52:51,782 --> 00:52:52,875
I can take you there.

736
00:52:52,951 --> 00:52:54,419
Thank you.

737
00:52:56,620 --> 00:52:57,953
Could we go now?

