764
00:55:00,386 --> 00:55:02,857
Well, she said
she hadn't heard from you.

765
00:55:04,756 --> 00:55:07,022
Walter, listen to me.

766
00:55:07,092 --> 00:55:08,527
She... She can't stay here.

767
00:55:08,594 --> 00:55:10,587
She doesn't know
anyone in New York.

768
00:55:10,662 --> 00:55:13,327
