to go back to Michigan.

769
00:55:15,101 --> 00:55:17,698
Okay. Okay, I'll try.

770
00:55:17,770 --> 00:55:19,033
Thank you, Walter.

771
00:55:20,773 --> 00:55:22,105
I have a note from her.

772
00:55:39,628 --> 00:55:40,789
