773
00:55:42,129 --> 00:55:43,462
No, thank you.

774
00:56:28,178 --> 00:56:29,111
Hello, sir.

775
00:56:29,179 --> 00:56:30,169
Hi.

776
00:56:32,783 --> 00:56:33,773
