01:35:40,233 --> 01:35:42,966
<i>now boarding at Gate 3 for Syria.</i>

1349
01:35:44,170 --> 01:35:48,167
<i>Delta flight 275, Gate 3 for Syria.</i>

1350
01:36:02,689 --> 01:36:04,318
Thank you, Walter.

1351
01:36:05,325 --> 01:36:06,692
Thank you for everything.

1352
01:36:08,029 --> 01:36:10,466
I don't want you to go.

1353
